advice_text_0.message:
By default Skyload stores all the files to the «Downloads» folder on your operation system.

Skyload cannot change the downloads destination folder, however, Skyload still can create its own folders in «Downloads» folder.

In case you wish to change the downloads destination folder this option is available in settings of your web-browser.

advice_text_1.message:
How to get a direct link to file?

In order to get a direct link to a file you need to launch Skyload download manager, then double click on the selected file, and then you would see the link opened in a new window.

You can copy it and start to download using other application.

advice_text_2.message:
How to remove a Save File pop-up window?

In order to hide the dialogue window you need to uncheck the respective option in settings of your web-browser.

advice_text_3.message:
